For Mac and Linux

1. Run bash deploy.sh DEPLOY_DIR (if no provided then defaults to new environment in /tmp) 

2. /tmp/conda/bin/anaconda login --username USERNAME --password PASSWORD

3. /tmp/conda/bin/anaconda upload /tmp/conda/conda-bld/osx-64/climextremes-0.2.0-py36_0.tar.bz2 --force (this should be output from deploy.sh)

4. Install conda install -c "CHANNEL" climextremes

